<a href="../man3/MPI_Status_f2c.3.php">MPI_Status_f2c</a>, <a href="../man3/MPI_Status_f2c.3.php">MPI_Status_f2c</a> - Translates a C status into a Fortran
INTEGER-style status, or vice versa.
<h2><a name='sect1' href='#toc1'>Syntax</a></h2>

